- Tuan Virat.

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:14.560
Oh ayolah!

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:18.960
Maksudku, kamu
baru saja mengakui

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:20.520
cintamu dan
mengungkapkan perasaanmu

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:24.120
